review.comment: From beginning to end we were very impressed with the service provided from Maxx Roof. They communicate with us well and followed up right away on everything. Thank you for the outstanding service!

Maxx roof was very professional, it only took one day to get the roof done. I was very happy with the outcome. Oh, and did I forget to mention that they installed hurricane straps and my house insurance went down by 30 percent! Yay 🙏🏼
Great service from the first call to the completion of repairs. The techs were professional and knowledgable throughout the process.
review.review_reply: Thank you for your feedback Timothy!
